msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/templating.rst:174
msgid ""
"If you want to add a hidden ``<input>`` tag containing a `CSRF token "
"<https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Security/"
"Types_of_attacks#cross-site_request_forgery_csrf>`_, you first need to "
"configure :ref:`CSRF protection <usage/middleware/builtin-middleware:csrf>`. "
"With that in place, you can now insert the CSRF input field inside an HTML "
"form:"
msgstr ""

