"middleware/builtin-middleware:csrf>` You can use this if you wish to insert "
"the ``csrf_token`` into non-HTML based templates, or insert it into HTML "
"templates not using a hidden input field but by some other means, for "
"example inside a special ``<meta>`` tag."
